revision_log_message.title: Revision log message
revision_log_message.description: Briefly describe the changes you have made.

status.title: Status
status.description: Indicates the status of the asset.

created.title: Authored on
created.description: The time that the asset was created.

changed.title: Changed
changed.description: The time the asset was last edited.

archived.title: Timestamp
archived.description: The time the asset was archived.

default_langcode.title: Default translation
default_langcode.description: A flag indicating whether this is the default translation.

revision_default.title: Default revision
revision_default.description: A flag indicating whether this was a default revision when it was saved.

revision_translation_affected.title: Revision translation affected
revision_translation_affected.description: Indicates if the last edit of a translation belongs to current revision.

flag.title: Flags
flag.description: Add flags to enable better sorting and filtering of records.

id_tag.title: ID tags
id_tag.description: List any identification tags that this asset has. Use the fields below to describe the type, location, and ID of each.

intrinsic_geometry.title: Intrinsic geometry
intrinsic_geometry.description: Add geometry data to this asset to describe its intrinsic location. This will only be used if the asset is fixed.

is_location.title: Is location
is_location.description: If this asset is a location, then other assets can be moved to it.

is_fixed.title: Is fixed
is_fixed.description: If this asset is fixed, then it can have an intrinsic geometry. If the asset will move around, then it is not fixed and geometry will be determined by movement logs.
